---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="我的資料平台">
    <section class="py-20 text-center text-white">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">資料平台</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">📊 整合各類金融、市場、資料分析工具，助你掌握資訊優勢。</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
            <a href="/table_daily" class="block bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 transition shadow text-left">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">📋 最新日況</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">快速查閱各類 CSV 資料、篩選與排序功能。</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/table" class="block bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 transition shadow text-left">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">📰 常用報表</h2>
            </a>
            <a href="/website" class="block bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 transition shadow text-left">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">💼 常用網頁</h2>

            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
